column2: SELECT TOP # p.ra AS ra, p.dec AS dec, p.flags, p.type, Photoz.z AS Photz, Photoz.zErr AS PhotzErr, SpecObj.z As Specz, SpecObj.zErr As SpeczErr, SpecObj.zWarning As zWarning, SpecObj.class As SpecClass, SpecObj.subClass As SpecsubClass, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z FROM PhotoObj AS p JOIN Photoz ON p.objID = Photoz.objID LEFT JOIN SpecObj On p.specObjID = SpecObj.specObjID WHERE (p.ra BETWEEN # AND #) AND (p.dec BETWEEN # AND #)
